20 Th\'fb-y\'ec: You take on the older one, I\'92ll take on the younger one.\
21 P\uc0\u97 \u772 -\u603 \u769 : Fine, fine.[6] That's how I had it planned anyway.\
22 Th\'fb-y\'ec: What about you, my friend?\
23 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : Me, you mean?\
24 Th\'fb-y\'ec: Yeah.\
25 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : I haven't even managed to have a proper talk [with anybody] yet!\
26 P\uc0\u97 \u772 -\u603 \u769 : Have a try at talking then. \
27 Th\'fb-y\'ec: Well, let's get going in a few minutes\'85 Oh, our friend is going to eat first now. Let's wait for him.\
