52 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : Then how do you continue with it after that? Do you talk about all sorts of things?\
53 Th\'fb-y\'ec: Well, after you've had your talk, you write letters to each other all day, and at night you go visit her. \
54 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : Which one is it that you say you'll marry? The one you visit all the time? \
55 Th\'fb-y\'ec: That guy[14] has taken her away from me now!\
56 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : Gee, there's no sense competing with each other like that, is there?[15]\
57 Th\'fb-y\'ec: Oh, that guy really causes people[16] a lot of trouble!\
