60 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : Wow, is this girl so beautiful then? Why is it that so many people are fighting over her?\
61 Th\'fb-y\'ec: Well, her body is beautiful. But her heart is fickle.[17] There's nothing that can be done with her right now. \
62 P\uc0\u97 \u772 -\u603 \u769 : Her body's beautiful, all right. But her heart is fickle.\
63 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : How old did you say she is?\
