73 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : Is that all? It couldn't be. It must be longer.\
74 Th\'fb-y\'ec: Well, there's still another part.\
75 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : Tell me all of it! I want to hear.\
76 Th\'fb-y\'ec: She says, "
\i You
\i0  probably don't think of 
