\i0  day and night. But I can't even eat from thinking about you!" For my part I write to her, "Oh, I think of you also day and night, whether I sleep or whether I sit.[23] But please, let us firmly resolve our hearts[24] and behave so that we may live together." \
77 P\uc0\u97 \u772 -\u603 \u769 : She'll say, "Even if I eat pure white rice, it is like chaff in my mouth! Even if I drink pure water, it is as though I drank a foul draught."[25]\
78 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : I see.\
79 Th\'fb-y\'ec: But some people just say those things with their mouths. In their hearts they're not in love.\
80 P\uc0\u97 \u772 -\u603 \u769 : Some people love with their body and soul, completely. Others may say it with their mouths, but it isn't so.\
81 Th\'fb-y\'ec: Well, let's go then! If you're through eating we'll go a-courting!\
82 P\uc0\u97 \u772 -\u603 \u769 : Let's go.\
