104 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : You say they're fickle, the Thai girls?\
105 Th\'fb-y\'ec: Very fickle, the Thai race.\
106 C\'e0-l\uc0\u596 \u770 : You say you can't lead them out into the woods?\
